These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, juice, coffee
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, ferret, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, jet-ski, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk  | coffee | juice    | soy-milk       |
| Pet         | cat | guinea-pig    | ferret      | hedgehog |
| Transport   | trike   | jet-ski | tram | train        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, tramrot, lemon, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, teacher, manager, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, train, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the manager is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the writer##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the person eating tramrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | lemon   | tramrot | cranberry     | pepper      |
| Job         | teacher | manager | project-manager | writer |
| Transport   | tram    | scooter   | train     | airplane      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing, drawing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, d&b, funk, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: german, chinese, spanish, american
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the chinese is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of funk##1
5. the american is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the american is on the right of the spanish##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | dancing | drawing | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | d&b    | disco | funk     |
| Nationality   | german | spanish    | american | chinese    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, nurse, lawyer, journalist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding, handball, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, van
1. the lawyer is the person driving the van##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the nurse is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is the lawyer##1
7. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
8. the journalist is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | doctor | journalist | lawyer | nurse |
| Sport       | skateboarding     | skiing      | cycling     | handball      |
| Transport   | bike | airplane         | van      | car        |

