.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, traveling, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, action, drama, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, cricket, rowing
1. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching action movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | traveling   | board-games | photography  | magic-tricks      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | family        | mystery  | action       |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket    | swimming | rowing |

