.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, social-worker, teacher, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, adventure, animation, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, techno, salsa, electronic
1. the architect is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the musician##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
5. the social-worker is on the far left##1
6. the person watching animation movies is the teacher##1
7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the musician is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | social-worker | teacher | musician | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | animation  | adventure | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | rock     | salsa | techno       |

