.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, artichoke, radish, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, writing, woodworking, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, family, comedy
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is the person eating radish##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | strawberry  | lime | radish   | artichoke     |
| Hobby         | reading | writing   | chess  | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | family         | scientific  | documentary | comedy  |

