.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, tea, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, spy, adventure, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, thai, spanish, mexican
1. the person drinking fanta is the spanish##1
2. the mexican is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the mexican is the person drinking tea##1
7. the thai is on the left of the mexican##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | tea     | mirinda | fanta |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | thriller | adventure       | spy    |
| Nationality   | thai   | mexican | indian    | spanish |

