.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, broccoli, banana, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, pop, folk, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, handball, swimming, snowboarding
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | banana        | asparagus   | broccoli  | spinach   |
| Music-Genre   | house         | gospel     | pop    | folk       |
| Sport         | handball | parkour | swimming | snowboarding |

