.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, milk
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, pineapple, cranberry
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, guinea-pig, snake
1. the person drinking milk is the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | soy-milk | milk | sprite        |
| Food       | cranberry | blueberry  | radish | pineapple     |
| Pet        | cat    | guinea-pig   | snake  | bird |

