.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, journalist, accountant, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, baseball, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, roller, taxi
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the roller##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | software-developer  | librarian | journalist  | accountant |
| Sport       | baseball | swimming        | skateboarding | climbing       |
| Transport   | helicopter   | bike          | taxi          | roller       |

