.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, baking, camping, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, comedy, spy, western
There are 4 different nationalities: french, nigerian, australian, colombian
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the colombian is on the left of the french##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the australian##1
7. the colombian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | camping   | singing | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | romance | comedy   | western |
| Nationality   | colombian     | french  | australian  | nigerian  |

