.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, sudoku, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, indie, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, water-polo, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving    | gardening        | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | indie     | reggae        | dubstep   |
| Sport         | cycling   | badminton | water-polo | basketball  |

