.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, musical, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, egyptian, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, van, scooter
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | epic  | disaster    | musical    |
| Nationality   | japanese | egyptian  | brazilian  | spanish |
| Transport     | scooter  | ship | van | airplane        |

