.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, sprite, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, adventure, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, lemonade-polo, basketball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person who's sport is lemonade-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta        | lemonade    | 7up | sprite      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | satire   | epic  | adventure  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | lemonade-polo | basketball   | snowboarding |

