The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, action, mystery, zombie
4 different pets are kept: goat, rat, chinchilla, frog
1. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person eating plum is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | zucchini     | cherry   | eggplant | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie | mystery | action   |
| Pet           | frog    | rat     | goat      | chinchilla     |

