.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, chef, mechanic, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, dubstep, salsa, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, indian, pakistani
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the indian##1
2. the chef is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the fan of salsa is the brazilian##1
5. the mechanic is on the far left##1
6. the accountant is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the indian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | mechanic  | doctor | chef  | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | trance       | dubstep | rock      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | colombian  | pakistani    | indian    |

