.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, thai, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, weightlifting, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, airplane, bus
1. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the thai is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | canadian | thai | japanese |
| Sport         | climbing | biathlon | snowboarding  | weightlifting  |
| Transport     | bike  | ship | bus     | airplane  |

