.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, mechanic, journalist
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, british, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, baseball, weightlifting, surfing
1. the entrepreneur is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
4. the british is on the far right##1
5. the brazilian is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the thai is on the far left##1
7. the journalist is on the far right##1
8. the thai is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | entrepreneur  | mechanic  | freelancer | journalist |
| Nationality   | thai   | brazilian | japanese   | british      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | weightlifting    | baseball   | surfing         |

 